Class StratmasObjectFactory

java.lang.Object
  StratmasClient.object.StratmasObjectFactory

public class StratmasObjectFactory
extends Object

StratmasObjectFactory is mapping of different sources of StratmasObjects to instances of the same.

addEventListener

public static void addEventListener(FactoryListener listener)
Registers the listener for notifications on StratmasObject-creation. Note that the implementation of this event class is geared towards long-term listeners, for transient listening, consider reimplementing the listener list.

Parameters:
listener - listener to add
